          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-02-18 11:55:01" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(a figurative extension of meaning of {L:στενάζω&lt;SDBG:στενάζω:000000&gt;}[a] ‘to groan, to sigh,’ {D:25.143}) to complain in an intensive and excessive manner</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to complain strongly</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It may even be possible to retain something of the figurative meaning of στενάζω in {S:05900500900004} by translating ‘do not complain with moaning’ or ‘do not moan and complain against.’</Comments>
